## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0c71a-104">受管理實體的存留期不會繫結至.NET 物件，表示它的存留期。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0c71a-104">The lifetime of a managed entity is not bound to the lifetime of the .NET object representing it.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0c71a-105">提供者可以使用標記有這個屬性的方法，來建立相對應的受管理實體的新執行個體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0c71a-105">The provider can use the method marked with this attribute to create a new instance of the corresponding managed entity.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0c71a-106">方法參數應該有相同的名稱和型別，做為類別繫結的建構函式的參數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0c71a-106">The method parameters should have the same name and type as the parameters of the class binding constructor.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0c71a-107">註冊存放庫中的 WMI 類別上，使用這個屬性並沒有任何影響。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0c71a-107">Use of this attribute does not have any affect on registration of the WMI class in the repository.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0c71a-108">它只適用於執行階段。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0c71a-108">It is only used at runtime.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="0c71a-109">下列範例示範如何使用 ManagementCreate 屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0c71a-109">The following example demonstrates how to use the ManagementCreate attribute.</span></span>  
  
```  
[ManagementEntity]  
public class ProcessInstance  
{  
     [ManagementKey]  
     public int Id;   
  
     [ManagementCreate]  
     public ProcessInstance StartProcess(string cmdLine)  
     {  
        ProcessInstance newProcess = new ProcessInstance(cmdLine);  
        newProcess.Start();  
        return newProcess;  
     }  
}  
```
